OL,3,CFormer PM Gordon Brown calls on Labour
OL,4,Cto scrap two-child benefit cap
OL,6,FGordon Brown has called for the two-
OL,7,Fchild benefit cap to be scrapped in an
OL,8,Fexclusive interview with ITV News
OL,9,FSocial Affairs Correspondent Sarah
OL,10,FCorker
OL,12,FFormer Prime Minister and Labour
OL,13,FChancellor Gordon Brown has put
OL,14,Fpressure on the government to scrap
OL,15,Fthe two-child benefit cap, describing
OL,16,Frising child poverty in the UK as a
OL,17,F"cancer in our society".
