OL,3,CFormer PM Gordon Brown calls on Labour
OL,4,Cto scrap two-child benefit cap
OL,6,F"You cannot have a situation where
OL,7,Funder a Labour government, child
OL,8,Fpoverty numbers just go up and up, and
OL,9,Fup," he said in an exclusive interview
OL,10,Fwith ITV News.
OL,12,FThe former political heavyweight has
OL,13,Fcalled on Chancellor Rachel Reeves to
OL,14,Fend the controversial policy that is
OL,15,Festimated to affect 1.5 million
OL,16,Fchildren across the country.
