OL,3,CFormer PM Gordon Brown calls on Labour
OL,4,Cto scrap two-child benefit cap
OL,6,F"You cannot leave unaddressed
OL,7,Fsomething that is a cancer in our
OL,8,Fsociety, which is children growing up
OL,9,Fand going to school ill clad and
OL,10,Fhungry," he told Social Affairs
OL,11,FCorrespondent Sarah Corker.
OL,13,F"I grew up in a town more than 50
OL,14,Fyears ago where I saw poverty at first
OL,15,Fhand. I never thought I'd see that
OL,16,Fkind of poverty again in my lifetime,
OL,17,Fbut now I'm seeing it again."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
