OL,3,CFormer PM Gordon Brown calls on Labour
OL,4,Cto scrap two-child benefit cap
OL,6,FThe cap, which was introduced under
OL,7,Fthe Conservative government, prevents
OL,8,Fmost families from claiming universal
OL,9,Fcredit or child tax credit for any
OL,10,Fthird or additional children born
OL,11,Fafter April 2017.
OL,13,F"What the Conservatives did was to
OL,14,Ftreat the third children as if they
OL,15,Fare second class citizens," Brown
OL,16,Fsaid. "But the needs of a third child,
OL,17,Fare exactly the same as the needs of
OL,18,Fthe first and second."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
