OL,3,CFormer PM Gordon Brown calls on Labour
OL,4,Cto scrap two-child benefit cap
OL,6,FOn coming into government last year,
OL,7,FLabour ministers said they did not
OL,8,Fhave the financial resources to lift
OL,9,Fthe cap and that it was "unaffordable"
OL,10,Fto do so.
OL,12,FThe issue has remained a source of
OL,13,Fdivision within the party, while
OL,14,Fexperts and charities have warned that
OL,15,F100 children are pulled into poverty
OL,16,Fevery day by the policy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
